<td class="positive">Yes</td>
<td class="negative">No</td>
<td class="positive">Yes</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="#locally-scoped">&#8220;Locally scoped&#8221; vocabulary terms</a></td>
<td class="positive">Yes, via vocab</td>
<td class="positive">Yes, via itemscope</td>
<td class="negative">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
